PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,FA number of people have since made
OL,7,Funfounded claims that they could be
OL,8,FBen.
OL,10,FOn Thursday Ben's mother, Kerry
OL,11,FNeedham, told ITV Calendar she is
OL,12,Fawaiting DNA test results after the
OL,13,Fsocial media page devoted to finding
OL,14,FBen was contacted by the girlfriend of
OL,15,Fa man allegedly bearing similarities
OL,16,Fto images of Ben.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,FMrs Needham said: "It's quite an
OL,7,Fanxious time for us all. We have been
OL,8,Fin this situation many times before.
OL,9,FWe just try to find a way to keep
OL,10,Fbusy, keep our emotions under control,
OL,11,Fyou don't want your hopes to run away
OL,12,Fwith you.
OL,14,F"After all these years, it's kind of
OL,15,Fbecome, without sounding too awful, an
OL,16,Felimination process. We can't ignore
OL,17,Fthese people that come forward - we
OL,18,Ftry to get enough information as
OL,19,Fpossible.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,F"If we can rule them out without a DNA
OL,7,Ftest, then that's all well and good.
OL,8,FBut if it comes down to having a DNA
OL,9,Ftest to put his mind at rest and our
OL,10,Fmind at rest, then that's the road we
OL,11,Fhave to go down."
OL,13,FShe said the man who had come forward
OL,14,Fappears similar to age-progression
OL,15,Fphotographs of Ben.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,F"He knows that he was adopted, and
OL,7,Fthere are lots of things that his
OL,8,Fadopted parents have told him that
OL,9,Fjust don't add up, and he is just
OL,10,Fdeeply suspicious about his upbringing
OL,11,Fand where he came from," she said.
OL,13,FBen vanished on 24 July 1991, while he
OL,14,Fwas playing outside a remote farmhouse
OL,15,Fwhich was being renovated by his
OL,16,Fgrandfather Eddie.
OL,18,FHis family, including Kerry's parents
OL,19,Fand two brothers, had moved to Kos
OL,20,Fearlier in the year to start a new
OL,21,Flife.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,FThere has been no sign of the toddler
OL,7,Fsince. Two excavations around the
OL,8,Ffarmhouse in 2012 and 2016 found no
OL,9,Fdefinitive proof of what happened.
OL,11,FAsked after all these years what kept
OL,12,Fher going, she said: "The truth and
OL,13,Fthe love for my son. I can't allow
OL,14,Fanyone to get away with this.
OL,16,F"We're not 100% sure what happened to
OL,17,FBen, but that's what keeps me going
OL,18,Fevery day. I need to find him or find
OL,19,Fout the truth as to what happened to
OL,20,Fhim, and if I don't keep doing this,
OL,21,Fthen no one else is."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,FShe added: "I appreciate the theory
OL,7,Fabout what South Yorkshire Police said
OL,8,Fafter their extensive excavation, but
OL,9,Fthere is still no physical, no
OL,10,Fforensic evidence to back that up, and
OL,11,Funtil I get that, Ben is still a
OL,12,Fmissing person and I will do whatever
OL,13,Fit takes to try to find him or at
OL,14,Fleast the answers of what happened to
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,F"You're living in torment every day
OL,7,Fthe not knowing. That's the most
OL,8,Fdifficult thing. You know, if a family
OL,9,Fmember is no longer alive, you can go
OL,10,Fthrough the grieving process and
OL,11,Feventually rebuild your life. But this
OL,12,F- it's ongoing agony. It is like
OL,13,Fliving in a constant nightmare you
OL,14,Fcan't wake up from.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,F"There isn't a day that goes by that
OL,7,FI'm not trying to keep the campaign
OL,8,Fgoing, keep up the publicity for Ben.
OL,9,FIt's the first thing I think about in
OL,10,Fthe morning when I wake up and the
OL,11,Flast thing I think about before I go
OL,12,Fto sleep at night: What else can I do?
OL,13,FWhere do I go from here?"
OL,15,FDiscussing the potential results of
OL,16,Fthe DNA test she said she felt
OL,17,F"apprehensive" and "anxious".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,FShe said: "I'm trying my best to keep
OL,7,Fmy emotions under control. I just keep
OL,8,Fbusy. It is there in the forefront of
OL,9,Fmy mind, but I have to do other
OL,10,Fthings. I have to keep the search
OL,11,Fgoing, keep the campaign going. If
OL,12,Fthis turns out to be negative, then
OL,13,Fwhat's the next step from here?"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774029954
OL,3,CMum awaits DNA results after man's
OL,4,Cclaim to be missing Ben Needham
OL,6,F"There are people, whether it be one
OL,7,Fperson or multiple people on the
OL,8,Fisland of Kos, who know exactly what's
OL,9,Fhappened to Ben, and I urge them to
OL,10,Fcome forward. Nothing can happen; no
OL,11,Fone can be arrested; nobody can go to
OL,12,Fprison because of the statute of
OL,13,Flimitations over there.
OL,15,F"I just want that person who knows
OL,16,Fexactly what happened to Ben to come
OL,17,Fforward and tell me. And then I can go
OL,18,Faway; I can leave their life alone; I
OL,19,Fcan leave their island alone. I won't
OL,20,Fkeep going back there once I know the
OL,21,Ftruth."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
